        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 3910 Stuart Road, Memphis, TN 38111 Finding the perfect home can be challenging, especially for seniors on a fixed income. Glendale Park Apartments is here to change that. Nestled in the heart of Memphis, this 13-story building is exclusively for those aged 55 and over who qualify as low to very low-income. With two spacious one-bedroom floor plans and stunning city views, Glendale Park is more than just an apartment—it's a community. Residents enjoy a vibrant lifestyle filled with monthly activities and inviting balconies for relaxation. Our professional management team is always ready to assist. Come visit us today and discover why so many seniors are proud to call Glendale Park their home. Apartment Features: High Speed Internet Access Walk-In Closets Patios/Balconies Full-Size Appliances Water, Sewer, Trash & Electric Included Community Features: Disability Access Green Community BBQ & Picnic Area Resident Lounge 24-Hour Automated Package Retrieval System Secured Access Elevator/s Laundry Facilities on Each Floor Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://livewithm2.com/g6j3va7n/glendale-park Pricing and availability are subject to change.",
